metadata.name: Our Pink World
metadata.description:
Artist: Erman Gulbag  
Title: Our Pink World  
Edition: Open

Our pink world may be dark, but the future is ours. We are the light that shines in the dark. We used to walk alone! Now we have hope, we are not alone. We have hearts on the road we walk. We have enough light to save our pink dreams from darkness. The only way this light exists is togetherness..
